message.content: a kitchen with dark gray cabinets and a tan marble countertop; a white refrigerator on the right side of the kitchen; a box of jello, a jar of jam, a box of salt, and a stack of plates on the kitchen counter; a dining table with a light brown top and white chairs, with a bottle of water, a box of crackers, and a mug on the table; a sink on the right side of the kitchen counter, next to a pot and a stove top; a range hood above the stove top; a doorway to the right of the dining table. the kitchen counter has various food items on it, including a box of "Chucky" cereal, a jar of jam, a box of jello, a box of rice bubbles, and a stack of plates. the dining table has a bottle of water, a box of crackers, a mug, and a wine glass on it. the room has white walls and a dark wood floor.
